"""" DRUPAL
Composer
https://github.com/composer/composer

Drush
https://github.com/drush-ops/drush

Upload Progess
https://www.drupal.org/node/793264

sudo apt-get install php5-dev
sudo pecl install uploadprogress

cd /etc/php5/apache2/conf.d
sudo touch uploadprogress.ini
sudo vim uploadprogress.ini
add the line "extension=uploadprogress.so" to uploadprogress.ini

sudo vim /etc/php5/apache2/php.ini
Add the line "extension=uploadprogress.so" to php.ini


